\begin{equation*}
L({\boldsymbol{A}}) - p({\boldsymbol{a}}) + p({\boldsymbol{b}}) \geq {L}( {\boldsymbol{C}} ).
\end{equation*}
\end{document} then the sequence from p(a) to the end of read (A) was retrieved. The sequence from the start of read (B) to p(b) was retrieved and connected to the above sequence to fill the gap. One hundred “N”s were inserted between two filled sequences to indicate a gap that could possibly be completed.
